<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُزَوِّجُهُمْ}</span> ... يَجْمَعُ لَهُ النَّوْعَيْنِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَقِيمًا}</span> ... لَا يُولَدُ لَهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٥١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَحْيًا}</span> ... إِعْلَامًا فِي المَنَام، أَوْ بِالإِلْهَامِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٥١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِن وَرَاءِ حِجَابٍ}</span> ... كَمَا كَلَّمَ مُوسَى - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَسُولًا}</span> ...<span class="c5"> هُوَ:</span> جِبْرِيلُ - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رُوحًا}</span> ... قُرْآنًا، سُمِّيَ القُرْآنُ رُوحًا؛ لِأَنَّهُ حَيَاةُ القُلُوبِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صِرَاطٍ مُّسْتَقِيمٍ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> هُوَ:</span> الإِسْلَامُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَصِيرُ}</span> ... تَرْجِعُ إِلَيْهِ، فَيُجَازِيكُمْ عَلَيْهَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>